<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='356000' id='t-356000'>What does the macro-data show us?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='358000' id='t-358000'>Well, the healthcare system has been transformed:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='361000' id='t-361000'>a culture pervaded with defensiveness,</span>
