<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='388000' id='t-388000'>That's enough to provide care to all the people</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='391000' id='t-391000'>in America who don't have it.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:44
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='393000' id='t-393000'>The trial lawyers say, &quot;Well, this legal fear</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='395000' id='t-395000'>makes doctors practice better medicine.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='397000' id='t-397000'>Well that's been studied too, by the Institute of Medicine</span>
