<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='402000' id='t-402000'>The fear has chilled professional interaction</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='405000' id='t-405000'>so thousands of tragic errors occur</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='408000' id='t-408000'>because doctors are afraid</span>
