<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='419000' id='t-419000'>Let's go to schools.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='421000' id='t-421000'>As we saw with the teacher in Cody, Wyoming,</span>
