<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='555000' id='t-555000'>Then, just staying above the Earth for one more second,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='558000' id='t-558000'>people are acting like idiots,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='561000' id='t-561000'>(Laughter)</span>
