<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='564000' id='t-564000'>(Applause)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='566000' id='t-566000'>Idiots. A couple of years ago,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='568000' id='t-568000'>Broward County, Florida, banned running at recess.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='572000' id='t-572000'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='573000' id='t-573000'>That means all the boys are going to be ADD.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='576000' id='t-576000'>I mean it's just absolutely</span>
