</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:51
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='580000' id='t-580000'>My favorite, though, are all the warning labels.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='582000' id='t-582000'>&quot;Caution: Contents are hot,&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='584000' id='t-584000'>on billions of coffee cups.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='586000' id='t-586000'>Archeologists will dig us up in a thousand years</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='589000' id='t-589000'>and they won't know about defensive medicine and stuff,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='592000' id='t-592000'>but they'll see all these labels, &quot;Contents are extremely hot.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='595000' id='t-595000'>They'll think it was some kind of aphrodisiac.</span>
